{"tid":1635314,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"成日都核彈核彈 要俾外國人知先叫核彈嘛","createTime":"2019-10-07T12:58:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T19:33:35.000Z","uid":53780,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c6385accbb23d4f6391213463cd82aa64447b37a","tid":1635314,"uid":53780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:58:50.000Z","msg":"我覺得我地有需要將6月9號到而家所有黑警打人 射人 私刑 酷刑 同埋 包庇黑社會 黑社會打人 既相同影片一次過整合哂開一個Twitter ac time line 擺好<br />\n<br />\n再不停宣傳個ac <br />\n心理學上如果一次過睇哂咁多警暴既影片同相，就算一個中立或者偏藍既人都會產生 同情 示威者同對黑警憤怒<br />\n<br />\n而且對通過美國人權法提供左大量佐證<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">開呢個post既目的 係想大家將手上有既圖同片掉哂出黎先</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n格式如下<br />\n日期:<br />\n相/片: (提醒你地最好save左d資料落電腦)<br />\ndescription:<br />\n受害者:<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 和理非既各位係時候為勇武做番d野</span>"},{"pid":"981e5791bff37d911a49b88398ba79b2453c86c7","tid":1635314,"uid":53780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:59:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fc64f250771112c7badbb82d8b3c38a5666c1a3c","tid":1635314,"uid":53780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:59:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe4fd9db236c2b1f27fcc1749dade50d038f02c1","tid":1635314,"uid":53780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:01:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eefc2f70cbbd2e8ec2ee9dac0d44c674c17ca8a4","tid":1635314,"uid":93383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:03:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1ViLb3Silul8PBEXq0rIxKNxlJdBtC8r6TCJ4Bs1exiA/edit#slide=id.g5e09edb7f7_93_46\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fpresentation%2Fd%2F1ViLb3Silul8PBEXq0rIxKNxlJdBtC8r6TCJ4Bs1exiA%2Fedit%23slide%3Did.g5e09edb7f7_93_46&d=2wHvujEsOXgOuf6ql2b4nP1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=e4fc01e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/presentati